## 📱 Responsive Design

### Breakpoints

| Name | Width | Target |
|------|-------|--------|
| Mobile | < 640px | Phones |
| Tablet | 640px - 1024px | iPads, small laptops |
| Desktop | > 1024px | Regular screens |
| Large | > 1440px | Large monitors |

